## What features are included in the free version vs. the subscription?

#### Free usage

- Sync with iCloud;
- The user can create and manage up to 2 focus plans;
- The user can protect the plan access with FaceID/TouchID;
- Block uninstallation of current apps;

#### With a subscription
- All features included in the Free usage;
- The user can create and manage up to 12 focus plans;
- Activate or deactivate any plan at any time;
- Access advanced features:
- Block installation of new apps;
- Block access to pre-specified websites.
